<title>没想到房子老龄化的程度会这么严重</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E8%99%8E%E5%97%85%E7%BD%91+%E6%B2%A1%E6%83%B3%E5%88%B0%E6%88%BF%E5%AD%90%E8%80%81%E9%BE%84%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E4%BC%9A%E8%BF%99%E4%B9%88%E4%B8%A5%E9%87%8D</link>
<content:encoded>&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;rich_media_thumb_wrp&quot; id=&quot;media&quot;&gt;

